<BaseLayout title = "Resume">
  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Profile</div>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-10 text-justify">
    I am a Bachelor in Computer Science with 2 years of experience with backend and frontend software development. 
    I have great passion in frontend web design and development, combined with my knowledge with graphic design tools for design and image creation.
    I am looking to gain experience in a professional environment whilst learning new technologies.
  </div>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Education</div>
  </div>

  <div class="time-line-container grid gap-4 mb-10">
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Bachelor of Computer Science"
      subtitle="2015 to 2022 at BINUS University, Tangerang, Indonesia"
    />
  </div>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Experience</div>
  </div>

  <div class="time-line-container mb-10">
    <TimeLineElement
      title="PT. Accelist Lentera Indonesia, Full Stack Developer"
      subtitle="From 2018 to 2019"
      desc="System multiplatform that includes the steps of a company's personnel, the structure and composition thereof, as well as a powerful designer of credentials and module of control of access. Outspread at the MINFAR and another entities of the country. Technologies: C++, Qt Framework, Subversión, Visual Paradigm, PostgreSQL, Jmeter"
