    <ul class="list-disc ml-4 my-2">
      <li>Create systems based on business modules.</li>
      <li>Create frontend pages for a business module based on design document</li>
      <li>Create backend logic, including database queries for the same module that is connected via REST API.</li>
      <li>Tech Stack: HTML, Typescript, C#, ASP.NET Core, AngularJS and SQL Server.</li>
    </ul>
  </TimeLineElement>
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Artlinks, Freelance Frontend Developer"
      subtitle="From 2020 to 2021"
    >
    I worked with Artlinks, a startup project aiming to create a platform for artists to share their work. Remote work due to COVID-19 pandemic.
    <ul class="list-disc ml-4 my-2">
      <li>Create a responsive website front-end using Vue.js based on client’s design.</li>
      <li>Helped input some page design with the designer.</li>
      <li>Tech Stack: HTML, SCSS, Javascript, Vue.js</li>
    </ul>   
